original_text: Welltower Announces Increase in Maximum Principal Amount of Tender Offer for its 3.950% Notes due 2023 and 3.750% Notes due 2023 and Welltower Announces a Cash Tender Offer for up to $300,000,000 aggregate principal amount of its 3.950% Notes due 2023 and 3.750% Notes due 2023
